How to install Z3 SAT Solver as a library?

find a place where you want to store the third party library (Preferrablly not
in STATICANALYSISLLVM repo, if so, please add it to gitignore)
git clone https://github.com/Z3Prover/z3.git
mkdir build
cmake -G "Unix Makefiles" ../
make -j4
make DESTDIR=/your/install/path install

The above commands shall give you the installation of Z3 library. Now we need to
tell STATICANALYSISLLVM repo where to find this library using:

cmake -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=/your/install/path ..
make

at the your build directory for this repo (i.e, the target of the cmake should
be the CMakeLists.txt in StaticAnalysis folder - the main cmake file). 
